Strouds May same - store sales fall . Strouds Inc said Thursday it had net sales of $ 15 . 8 million for the four weeks ended May 31 , compared with $ 14 . 7 million a year earlier . Comparable - store sales were down 7 . 3 percent . Net sales for the 13 weeks ended May 31 were $ 50 . 5 million , compared with $ 46 . 4 million a year earlier . comparable - store sales fell 5 . 0 percent . 
